Simply manage paths.

## Install

```
npm install pathname-js
```

## Usage

```javascript
var pathname = new Pathname("some/path/with/an/:id");
pathname.string;
// => "some/path/with/an/:id"

pathname[2] = 'to';
pathname[3] = 'number';
pathname.id = 4;
pathname.string;
// => "some/path/to/number/4"

pathname.concat('and', 'letter/:letter');
pathname.letter = 'A';
pathname.string;
// => "some/path/to/number/4/and/letter/A"
```

